    "long_instructions": "##Accessibility Issues\r\n- Inspect the page and **identify 2–3 accessibility issues**.\r\n    - Use **POUR framework** from your Activity Guide to categorize issues.\r\n    - Example: *Low-contrast text → Perceivable issue.*\r\n- Use the **Accessibility Prompt Builder** (“mad libs” style templates in your Activity Guide) to write AI prompts that propose fixes.\r\n    - Example template: *“Ensure all text has a color contrast ratio of at least 4.5:1 against its background.”*\r\n- Run the prompt in the AI.\r\n- Save your prompts to **Backpack** as artifacts.",
